# NETWORK::NETWORK_ENTITY_AREA_IS_OCCUPIED

## Parameters
* **INT** areaID

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Checks if this area is occupied on any machine
The areaID is the ID returned by NETWORK_ADD_ENTITY_AREA
